text: Hyppeln, an island in the Gothenburg northern archipelago Hyppeln is a Swedish island in the archipelago of Gothenburg, part of Öckerö Municipality. It is about long. "Hyppeln" is also the name of the village on the island, which has about 150 permanent residents. There is a shop and a guest harbour on the island. ==External links== *Hyppelns IK Category:Islands of Västra Götaland County Category:Populated places in Västra Götaland County Category:Öckerö Municipality
